																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								                            investment. Join us to start trading today!
							</p>

							<ul class="section-list">

								<li class="section-item">
									<div class="title-wrapper">
										<i class="fas fa-check-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>

										<h3 class="h3 list-title">Discover real-time stock prices</h3>
									</div>

									<p class="item-text">
										Explore a variety of trading options with our platform. Whether you prefer																																																																																																																																																																																				                                    traditional stock trading, options, we offer a range
																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						                                    of tools to suit your needs. Join us today and seize control of your financial
