									</p>
								</li>

								<li class="section-item">
									<div class="title-wrapper">
										<i class="fas fa-check-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>

										<h3 class="h3 list-title">
											Trade stocks effortlessly with Prosync</h3>
									</div>

									<p class="item-text">
										Enjoy various trading options like Spot Trade, Futures Trade, Staking
